# simulated-signing.md is generated by `npm run package` (via the
# packageAfterCopy hook in forge.config.ts) whenever no Apple Developer
# creds are in the env. We INTENTIONALLY track it in git: the test
# (BT-L5-5) asserts its presence, and the content documents the simulated-
# vs-real signing flow. Subsequent regenerations may produce identical
# bytes; a real diff would indicate the hook's content changed.
# (No gitignore entry — track it.)
